RACE.RACE_TEXT: RETAMA PARK RACE 1 7F Dirt CR: 81. Allowance Purse 20000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 123 lbs.; Older, 125 lbs. (Highest Earnings 2022-2023 Preferred).
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PEARLS SPIRIT AA tracked in the three path, swung out to the seven path turning into the lane, and inched past an inner pair in the closing stages. AA SWEET VICTORY vied for the lead inside, drifted out leaving the chute, was driven from the rail around the turn, floated out to the four path into the stretch, and ran on to hold place. TM PURNCESS dueled for the lead in the five path, took a clear advantage from the three path into the turn, held on to a short lead while in the five path entering the stretch, but faded in the final furlong for show. WMA BIG BABY pressed the pace betwen foes in the four path, but lost ground around the turn, and was one paced. UPTOWN LADY ARABELLA clipped heels leaving the chute, raced off the pace in the five path and couldn't make an impact. AA RICH WHISKEY had an awkward start, dropped off the pace in the four path but was no menace. AFTER A STEWARDS INQUIRY, AA SWEET VICTORY WAS DISQUALIFIED FROM SECOND AND PLACED FIFTH FOR DRIFTING OUT LEAVING THE CHUTE, CAUSING UPTOWN LADY ARABELLA TO CLIP HEELS. THIS RACE WAS ALSO HAND TIMED.
